                <h1>Change Background Color on Instagram Stories Made Easy</h1>
                <p>To change the background color on your Instagram Story, open the app and create a new story. After taking a photo or video, tap on the brush icon at the top right. Choose a color from the palette or use the dropper tool to select a color from your image. Then, hold your finger on the screen to apply the background color!</p>
